## Proposed Changes

### Database — Prisma Schema

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/isyaa/OneDrive/Documents/Web%20and%20Code/4Persona/backend/prisma/schema.prisma)

Tambahkan 2 model baru:

```prisma
// ─── Konfigurasi Voucher (1 baris, dikelola admin) ────────
model VoucherConfig {
  id              Int      @id @default(1)
  isEnabled       Boolean  @default(false)  // Toggle ON/OFF global
  voucherCode     String   @default("")     // Kode voucher Shopee (misal VUNPERSONA20)
  discountLabel   String   @default("")     // Label diskon (misal "Diskon 20%")
  totalStock      Int      @default(0)      // Stok total voucher
  claimedCount    Int      @default(0)      // Jumlah yang sudah di-claim
  expiryHours     Int      @default(72)     // Masa berlaku voucher per user (default 3 hari = 72 jam)
  shopeeUrl       String   @default("")     // URL redirect ke Shopee
  updatedAt       DateTime @updatedAt

  @@map("voucher_config")
}

// ─── Catatan Klaim Voucher per User ───────────────────────
model VoucherClaim {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId      String   @unique  // 1 user = 1 claim seumur hidup
  user        User     @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  voucherCode String              // Snapshot kode saat di-claim
  claimedAt   DateTime @default(now())
  expiresAt   DateTime            // claimedAt + expiryHours

  @@map("voucher_claims")
}
```

Tambahkan relasi di model `User`:
```prisma
model User {
  // ... existing fields ...
  voucherClaim VoucherClaim?  // 1-to-1 optional
}
```

Setelah update schema, jalankan:
```bash
npx prisma migrate dev --name add-voucher-system
```

