### Backend — NestJS Vouchers Module

#### [NEW] `backend/src/vouchers/vouchers.module.ts`
Module NestJS yang mengekspos `VouchersService` dan `VouchersController`.

#### [NEW] `backend/src/vouchers/vouchers.service.ts`
Service dengan method berikut:

| Method | Deskripsi |
|--------|-----------|
| `getConfig()` | Return konfigurasi voucher (admin) |
| `getPublicConfig()` | Return info publik: `isEnabled`, `remainingStock`, `discountLabel` (TANPA kode voucher) |
| `updateConfig(dto)` | Update konfigurasi: kode, stok, label, URL, toggle on/off (admin) |
| `claimVoucher(userId)` | Claim voucher untuk user — cek: (1) sistem enabled, (2) stok tersedia, (3) user belum pernah claim. Return `VoucherClaim` |
| `getMyVoucher(userId)` | Get voucher milik user yang login. Return claim + kode + expired status |

#### [NEW] `backend/src/vouchers/vouchers.controller.ts`
REST endpoints:

| Route | Guard | Method |
|-------|-------|--------|
| `GET /api/vouchers/public` | — (public) | `getPublicConfig()` — untuk homepage promo banner |
| `GET /api/vouchers/my` | `JwtAuthGuard` | `getMyVoucher()` — untuk profile page |
| `GET /api/admin/vouchers/config` | `JwtAuthGuard + AdminGuard` | `getConfig()` — admin panel |
| `PUT /api/admin/vouchers/config` | `JwtAuthGuard + AdminGuard` | `updateConfig()` — admin panel |
| `GET /api/admin/vouchers/claims` | `JwtAuthGuard + AdminGuard` | `getClaims()` — daftar user yang sudah claim |

